<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Dear Currency Center users,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">In order to ensure complete and accurate reporting of the monthly currency repatriation report, we would be grateful for your time to fill in our data collection regarding blocked funds.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">It is very important that you report back to us :</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li>Amount blocked in respective currencies as at month end</li><li>Allocation amounts received</li><li>Any on ground activities/discussions being carried out from your end to unlock blocked funds situation.</li><li>Any specific topic/subject matter you would like a particular focus on</li></ul></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Please ensure you provide us with complete information by latest <b>14th&nbsp;</b></font><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>{!CASE(MONTH(TODAY()),1,'January',2,'February',3,'March',4,'April',5,'May',6,'June',7,'July',8,'August',9,'September',10,'October',11,'November',12,'December','')}</b></span><font face="arial">. <b>Your participation is essential to IATA Currency Repatriation advocacy efforts</b>.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Should you have any queries or more feedback, please log a case in your IATA Customer Portal under the topic "Currency Center".</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">Currency Center Team</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">You can find Monthly Survey <a href="https://ccf2-customer-portal-iata.cs106.force.com/ISSP_CurrencyCenterReportingActionsMonth?id={!Currency_Center_Survey__c.Id}">here</a>.</font></div>]]></td>
